things out of wood or linoleum and made pictures.

00:03:47.290 --> 00:03:51.160
And then they would ink up the linoleum plate
and they would put paper or fabric on them

00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:53.130
and they would step on it.

00:03:53.130 --> 00:03:56.750
And they would peel off the paper or fabric.

00:03:56.750 --> 00:03:58.370
And this is the art they created.

