00:05:13.270 --> 00:05:15.290
This is Virginia Burton.

00:05:15.290 --> 00:05:23.210
She was an amazing, joyful, vivacious person
that people loved to be around.

00:05:23.210 --> 00:05:27.280
She made people smile just by being the personality
she was.

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:32.980
