big, spectacular parties.

00:05:32.980 --> 00:05:34.610
And she loved her garden.

00:05:34.610 --> 00:05:40.210
And they inspired her to create her art.

00:05:40.210 --> 00:05:42.310
And she loved animals.

00:05:42.310 --> 00:05:47.630
And that also inspired her.

00:05:47.630 --> 00:05:53.040
But mostly she loved -- because she was a
mom -- can you guess?

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.380
Her boys.

00:05:54.380 --> 00:05:56.000
She had two sons.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:57.420
Aristides, her oldest.

