00:06:23.580 --> 00:06:26.270
So we both really love trains too.

00:06:26.270 --> 00:06:28.710
And Aristides liked trains.

00:06:28.710 --> 00:06:34.330
So Jinnee wrote a book for Aristides called
-- what is it called?

00:06:34.330 --> 00:06:36.520
"Choo Choo."

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:40.450
And Michael loved steam shovels.

00:06:40.450 --> 00:06:45.300
This is a steam shovel -- an actual steam
shovel from a long time ago.

00:06:45.300 --> 00:06:52.210
And Jinnee looked at the steam shovels and
she created -- do any of you know this book?

00:06:52.210 --> 00:06:53.800
Mike Mulligan -- you have it?

00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:54.800
Well, that's awesome.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:57.540
It's such a great story.

