very simply, she's made up of a bunch of shapes.

00:23:03.280 --> 00:23:06.240
And I think you guys all know how to draw
a circle.

00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:07.240
Right?

00:23:07.240 --> 00:23:08.539
And do you know how to draw a rectangle?

00:23:08.539 --> 00:23:09.539
Yeah.

