Is that what you're saying?

00:23:14.820 --> 00:23:15.820
[laughter] Oh, okay.

00:23:15.820 --> 00:23:20.870
I'm just going to quickly draw the shapes
so you guys can draw it at home.

00:23:20.870 --> 00:23:22.059
Okay?

